font-size: x-small;\">o</span><br />\n蓋集中營係逼不得已，係班人唔聽話，殺中國人，<br />\n共匪咁做都係保護我地，咩叫路西法效應？資訊戰？<br />\n民權？極左民族主義？我地唔識，我淨係知你地搞到人地返工（包括我），其他野我見唔到我唔知，你好煩，信唔信我打柒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">o</span>"},{"pid":"b69053dd26a9a37aa2d3a55c4925ec8ee14f6b62","tid":1726471,"uid":310883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f39626dcb9d796462b820e0d361bc515f8d8e65a","tid":1726471,"uid":182508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2a5b75e28846c4e7bfa058a8b69b8ddf82fc0ff","tid":1726471,"uid":310883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daee7cc79559abdd721c2b6ff21ad8ad6b106dc3","tid":1726471,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:25:09.000Z","msg":"你阻路只會民意愈黎愈唔支持我地<br />\n睇下幾多人清緊路障嘈緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:36:08.000Z","msg":"個啲藍絲嚟架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會有少少影響 不過主要係無出過嚟遊行既港豬同中立撚<br />\n對個二百萬有出開嚟遊行既應該唔太大影響"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:58:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:09:02.000Z","msg":"唔怕 其實最影響都市民既中大都解封左<br />\n所以以家根本唔會有問題"}]}